lead_paragraph: CORENMAN--Leonard. Alpine Country Club, its Officers, Board of Governors, Members and Staff deeply mourn the passing of its former Member, and offer our deepest condolences to the entire Corenman and Margaritis families. Alpine Country Club 1/3
